==Useful Info==
'''Starflowers''' are [[Abyss]]al plants with dangerous reaching attacks. They can reach up to 3 tiles away, similar to the [[Rift]] unrand.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
* Like most stationary monsters, they aren't a threat if you stay outside of their range. However, they mostly appear in [[vault]]s, often guarding the rune.

==History==
*Starflowers were introduced in [[0.29]].
